OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud affecting many in
OL,6,Fthe morning, clear for others. A
OL,7,Fbright and sunny afternoon to follow
OL,8,Ffor most. Breezy, especially along the
OL,9,Fcoast. Above average temperatures,
OL,10,Fcooler by the sea.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear evening for many.
OL,13,FCoastal low cloud returning to affect
OL,14,Fmany places overnight, remaining dry
OL,15,Fwith a gentle northeasterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
