OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy in the early morning
OL,6,Ffor many but soon becoming bright with
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine as the cloud retreats. A
OL,8,Fgentle northeasterly breeze persists
OL,9,Fthroughout the day, stronger along the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,13,Fspells and cloudy periods. The
OL,14,Fnortherly breeze introduces a fresher
OL,15,Ffeel, especially along coasts where it
OL,16,Fremains windy. Temperatures returning
OL,17,Fto around average by the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
